div.p:
And the publican standing a far of, would not so much as
lift his eies toward heauen: but he ⸫ knocked his brest, saieng;
God be mercifull to me a sinner.

By this word are ment all priuate men, for it is euident that
except they vnderstoode the publike praier and thankesgiuing,
they could not shew foorth their assent by saieng, Amen.
